<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="auto">

<body>
    <main>
        <div class="container-fluid py-2 p-0" style="background-color: #006400; color: white;">
            <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-body-tertiary rounded-3 position-relative" style="height: 500px;">
                <!-- Set a fixed height for the container -->
                <div class="container-fluid py-5 px-0 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center h-100">
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">LockBox</h1>
                        <p class="fs-4">Secure your digital life, anywhere <br> and anytime, with LockBox – your trusted guardian <br /> for passwords and sensitive information.</p>
                        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="CreateAccount" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="button" style="background-color: white; color: darkgreen; border-color: darkgreen;">Create an account</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 bottom-0" style="width: 50%;">
                        <img src="~/lib/images/businessPeople.jpg" alt="LockBox" class="right-image">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>






      <h1 class="visually-hidden">Features examples</h1>

        <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="hanging-icons">
            <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Everything you need</h2>
            <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
                <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
                    <div class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                        <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#toggles2" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Easy</h3>
                        <img src="~/lib/images/iconTime.png" alt="Image Description">
                        <p>For those who aim higher, protect better, and work together, LockBox is quick and simple to set up for individuals and teams.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
                    <div class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                        <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#cpu-fill" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Convenient</h3>
                        <img src="~/lib/images/iconConvenient.png" alt="Image Description">
                        <p>Convenient cross-platform access for mobile and browser apps. Secure and simple, wherever you are.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
                    <div class="icon-square text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                        <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#tools" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">Secure</h3>
                        <img src="~/lib/images/iconSafe.png" alt="Image Description">
                        <p>LockBox's open-source philosophy is rooted in zero-knowledge, end-to-end encryption, ensuring trust, accountability, and security in every step.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        

        <div class="container py-3">        
            <main>
                <div class="pricing-header p-3 pb-md-4 mx-auto text-center">
                    <h1 id="pricing" class="display-4 fw-normal text-body-emphasis">Pricing</h1>
                    <p class="fs-5 text-body-secondary">Choose the plan that fits your needs.</p>
                </div>
        
                <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 mb-3 text-center">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-header py-3">
                                <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Free</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title">$0<small class="text-body-secondary fw-light">/mo</small></h1>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
                                    <li>Unlimited devices</li>
                                    <li>All core functions</li>
                                    <li>Always free</li>
                                    <li>Help center access</li>
                                </ul>
                                <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="CreateAccount" type="button" class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-outline-primary" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #006400; border-color: #006400;">Sign up for free</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-header py-3">
                                <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Pro</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title">$1<small class="text-body-secondary fw-light">/mo</small></h1>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
                                    <li>File attachments</li>
                                    <li>Emergency access</li>
                                    <li>Security reports</li>
                                    <li>Priority e-mail support</li>
                                </ul>
                                <button style="background-color: darkgreen" type="button" class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary">Get started</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm" style="border-color: darkgreen;">
                            <div class="card-header py-3 text-bg-primary">
                                <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">Enterprise</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title">$4<small class="text-body-secondary fw-light">/mo</small></h1>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
                                    <li>Secure data sharing</li>
                                    <li>Event log monitoring</li>
                                    <li>Directory integration</li>
                                    <li>Account recovery</li>
                                </ul>
                                <button type="button" style="background-color: darkgreen" class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary">Contact us</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="/docs/5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/docs/5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>